OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776780668
OL,3,CBeavers successfully reintroduced to
OL,4,CEast Sussex for first time in 400 years
OL,6,FBeavers have been successfully
OL,7,Freintroduced to East Sussex for the
OL,8,Ffirst time in 400 years as part of a
OL,9,Fnew wildlife project.
OL,11,FFive beavers were moved from an
OL,12,Finfrastructure development site in
OL,13,FScotland and released in woodland near
OL,14,FBowyers Wood.
OL,16,FThe woodland was selected as it is
OL,17,Fbelieved to be a former home for
OL,18,Fbeavers before they were hunted to
OL,19,Fextinction in the United Kingdom.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
