PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776780668
OL,3,CBeavers successfully reintroduced to
OL,4,CEast Sussex for first time in 400 years
OL,6,FBusinessman Dale Vince and broadcaster
OL,7,FChris Packham are backing the project,
OL,8,Fled by Ecotalk, which is working in
OL,9,Fcollaboration with the Beaver Trust to
OL,10,Frestore nature.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FMr Vince said the release of the
OL,18,Fbeavers represents a "big moment and
OL,19,Fsmall step all at the same time".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
