PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776780668
OL,3,CBeavers successfully reintroduced to
OL,4,CEast Sussex for first time in 400 years
OL,6,FHe said: "Beavers are the Swiss Army
OL,7,Fknife of re-wilding - they create
OL,8,Famazing habitats that will help us
OL,9,Frestore Britain's wildlife, they help
OL,10,Fprevent flooding and their work
OL,11,Freduces carbon emissions - helping us
OL,12,Ftowards net zero."
OL,14,FMr Packham, who is Ecotalk's chief
OL,15,Fecologist, added the release went
OL,16,F"brilliantly", expressing his thanks
OL,17,Fto the "Beaver Trust and all the
OL,18,FEcotalk staff and volunteers".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
